meu amor.

53
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,640
Tudo o que quiseres, Pablito.

54
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,680
Tudo o que eu quiser?

55
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:16,140
Sim, meu amor, o que for.

56
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,770
De certeza?

57
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,250
Então...

58
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:42,540
